msgctxt "chunk_E6E8A1D1"
msgid "`pip install -U pdf2zh`\n\n"
msgstr "`pip install -U pdf2zh`\n\n"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 27
msgctxt "chunk_9FB0E3EA"
msgid "## The following files do not exist: example.pdf"
msgstr "## Los siguientes archivos no existen: example.pdf"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 52
msgctxt "chunk_22B1E6C4"
msgid "- **Issue**:  "
msgstr "- **Problema**:"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 29
msgctxt "chunk_FAB807CC"
msgid "When executing the program, users would have the following outputs: `The following files do not exist: example.pdf` if the document was not found.\n"
msgstr "Al ejecutar el programa, los usuarios tendrían las siguientes salidas: `Los siguientes archivos no existen: example.pdf` si el documento no se encontró.\n"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 31
msgctxt "chunk_E7371FD6"
msgid "- **Solution**:\n  - Open the command line in the directory where the file is located, or\n  - Enter the full path of the file directly after pdf2zh, or\n  - Use the interactive mode `pdf2zh -i` to drag and drop files directly\n\n"
msgstr "- **Solución**:\n  - Abre la línea de comandos en el directorio donde se encuentra el archivo, o\n  - Ingresa la ruta completa del archivo directamente después de pdf2zh, o\n  - Usa el modo interactivo `pdf2zh -i` para arrastrar y soltar archivos directamente\n\n"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 37
msgctxt "chunk_F523458B"
msgid "## SSL Error and Other Network Issues"
msgstr "## Error de SSL y otros problemas de red"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 39
msgctxt "chunk_DF99BBC1"
msgid "When downloading hugging face models, users in China may get network error. For example, in [issue #55](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/issues/55), [#70](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/issues/70).\n"
msgstr "Al descargar modelos de hugging face, los usuarios en China pueden experimentar errores de red. Por ejemplo, en [issue #55](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/issues/55), [#70](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/issues/70).\n"

# This content is from "FAQ.md", line 41
msgctxt "chunk_AC4D20E5"
msgid "- **Solution**:\n  - [Bypass GFW](https://github.com/clash-verge-rev/clash-verge-rev).\n  - [Use Hugging Face Mirror](https://hf-mirror.com/).\n  - [Use Portable version](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next?tab=readme-ov-file#method-ii-portable).\n  - [Use Docker instead](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next#docker).\n  - [Update Certificates](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/51925384/unable-to-get-local-issuer-certificate-when-using-requests), as suggested in [issue #55](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/issues/55).\n"
msgstr "- **Solución**:\n  - [Bypass GFW](https://github.com/clash-verge-rev/clash-verge-rev).\n  - [Usar espejo de Hugging Face](https://hf-mirror.com/).\n  - [Usar versión portable](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next?tab=readme-ov-file#method-ii-portable).\n  - [Usar Docker en su lugar](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next#docker).\n  - [Actualizar certificados](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/51925384/unable-to-get-local-issuer-certificate-when-using-requests), como se sugiere en [issue #55](https://github.com/PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next/issues/55).\n"

